'''超越肉類公司'''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://bw.businessweekly.com.tw/press/content.php?id=23936|title=商周獨家呈現「未來之宴」 110位重量級貴賓搶鮮品嚐雞肉2.0 預見飲食革命新浪潮|work=商周集團|accessdate=2017-03-17|archive-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317233852/http://bw.businessweekly.com.tw/press/content.php?id=23936|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ettoday.net/news/20140307/332084.htm|title=「無雞肉」雞柳條騙了美食作家　幕後英雄是台灣人|date=2014-03-07|agency=東森新聞雲|accessdate=2017-03-17|archive-date=2017-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170317145028/http://www.ettoday.net/news/20140307/332084.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>（{{lang-en|Beyond Meat}}）是洛杉磯一家製造100%[[植物肉|全植物成分的肉類替代品]]的製造商。自2013年開始，該公司產品已可在美國全國的[[全食超市|全食超市]]購買<ref name="Flanagan2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/fake-chicken-beef-meat-from-plants-2014-7|title=This Fake Meat Is So Good It Fooled Whole Foods Customers For 3 Days|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Flanagan, Graham|date=7 July 2014|publisher=Business Insider|archive-date=2017-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170416193457/http://www.businessinsider.com/fake-chicken-beef-meat-from-plants-2014-7|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Strickland2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.inc.com/julie-strickland/ethan-brown-beyond-meat-wired-conference.html|title=Fake Meat for the Masses?|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Julie Strickland|date=05/07/2013|publisher=Inc|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506105222/https://www.inc.com/julie-strickland/ethan-brown-beyond-meat-wired-conference.html|archive-date=2019-05-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

該公司於2009年創立，首任總裁為伊森·布朗，其投資人包括[[凯鹏华盈|凱鵬華盈]]、風投公司[[Twitter|Obvious Corporation]]、[[比爾·蓋茲|比爾·蓋茲]]、[[比兹·斯通|比兹·斯通]]與美國人道協會<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=125495|title=未來食物？蔬菜變肉口感逼真 台灣創意熱銷美國 {{!}} 節目 {{!}} 三立新聞網 SETN.COM|accessdate=2017-04-04|last=三立新聞網|archive-date=2017-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404215530/http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=125495|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 起源 ==
總裁伊森·布朗於2009年創立「超越肉類」公司（原「薩維奇河公司」），主要致力於生產純植物性成分之仿肉食品，以消除肉品業的生產過程所造成的負面影響。<ref name="Foster2013" /><ref name="Gunther2013">{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2013/10/03/the-bill-gates-backed-company-thats-reinventing-meat/|title=Beyond Meat closes in on the perfect fake chicken, turns heads, tastebuds|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Marc Gunther|date=Oct 3, 2013|publisher=Fortune|archive-date=2014-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031145230/http://fortune.com/2013/10/03/the-bill-gates-backed-company-thats-reinventing-meat/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Chang2014" /><ref name="Barker2012">{{cite web|url=http://www.columbiatribune.com/news/local/chicken-substitute-to-be-made-in-columbia/article_1424b83c-17a0-5319-91e2-fee26bf59ecc.html|title=Chicken substitute to be made in Columbia|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Jacob Barker|date=Aug 7, 2012|publisher=Columbia Tribune}}</ref>布朗成立「超越肉類」的靈感啟發來自於他口中的「雞之國」，那是他小時候週末常去度假的自家農場，位在鄰近賓夕法尼亞州邊界的馬里蘭州鄉村地區。<ref name="Noguchi2012" />

布朗一開始便與[[密苏里大学|密蘇里大學]]兩位教授謝富弘<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC-%E5%A4%9A%E6%B1%81-%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%A0%E9%9B%9E%E8%82%89-%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-133400006.html|title=台專家研發　多汁「人造雞肉」在美上市|publisher=TVBS|accessdate=2014-03-07|language=zh-TW|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140311102519/http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B0%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC-%E5%A4%9A%E6%B1%81-%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%A0%E9%9B%9E%E8%82%89-%E5%9C%A8%E7%BE%8E%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-133400006.html|archivedate=2014-03-11}}</ref>和哈羅德‧赫夫接洽，倆人在提煉植物蛋白方面的研究已有多年。<ref name="Kile2014">{{cite web|url=http://america.aljazeera.com/watch/shows/techknow/blog/2014/1/15/need-to-know-tasteslikechickenmadeinalab.html|title=Need to Know: Tastes like chicken, made in a lab|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Meredith Kile|date=Jan 15, 2014|publisher=Aljazeera America|archive-date=2014-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140803023231/http://america.aljazeera.com/watch/shows/techknow/blog/2014/1/15/need-to-know-tasteslikechickenmadeinalab.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>兩位教授花了將近十年的時間在大學的實驗室裡，測試在不同溫度和壓力下提煉混合大豆和豌豆蛋白，期望能夠做出無論外觀或質感都最類似真的雞肉的植物蛋白。後來，謝富弘和哈羅德‧赫夫教授又花了五年的時間才做出「超越肉類」第一個商品的配方，也就是2012年，超越肉類公司在限定地區所推出的「無雞肉之雞柳條」。<ref name="Hurley2014">{{cite web|url=http://blogs.riverfronttimes.com/gutcheck/2014/06/beyond_meat_it_tastes_like_chicken_sort_of.php|title="Beyond Meat," the Mizzou-Creared Faux Chicken That Fooled the New York Times|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Patrick J. Hurley|date=Jun 27, 2014|publisher=Riverfront Times|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20161206200418/http://blogs.riverfronttimes.com/gutcheck/2014/06/beyond_meat_it_tastes_like_chicken_sort_of.php|archivedate=2016年12月6日}}</ref><ref name="Manjoo2012">{{cite web|url=http://www.slate.com/articles/technology/technology/2012/07/beyond_meat_fake_chicken_that_tastes_so_real_it_will_freak_you_out_.html|title=Fake Meat So Good it Will Freak You Out|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Farhad Manjoo|date=Jul 2012|publisher=Slate|archive-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330032620/http://www.slate.com/articles/technology/technology/2012/07/beyond_meat_fake_chicken_that_tastes_so_real_it_will_freak_you_out_.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

布朗曾經說過，公司的長程目標是製造出一個商品能夠用來滿足全球持續成長中肉品需求的市場，特別是像[[印度|印度]]和[[中國|中國]]這樣的市場。<ref name="Flanagan2014" /><ref name="Manjoo2012" />

== 歷史沿革 ==
伊森‧布朗於2009年創立「超越肉類」作為解決個人所認知的肉品業所帶來的問題的可能方法。<ref name="Kanani2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/rahimkanani/2014/03/06/the-future-of-meat-is-meatless-just-as-tasty-and-about-to-change-the-world/|title=The Future of Meat is Meatless, Just as Tasty, And About to Change the World|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Rahim Kanani|date=03/06/2014|publisher=Forbes|archive-date=2016-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208011922/http://www.forbes.com/sites/rahimkanani/2014/03/06/the-future-of-meat-is-meatless-just-as-tasty-and-about-to-change-the-world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

超越肉品公司在2012年第一次推出「無雞肉之雞柳條」時，僅限[[北加州|北加州]]全食超市能購買到<ref name="Manjoo2012" />。之後不久，公司開始擴大生產設備，預計要在產品目錄中增加「無肉之絞細牛肉」和「無肉之絞細豬肉」等品項。<ref name="Noguchi2012">{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/blogs/thesalt/2012/05/17/152519988/a-farmer-bets-better-fake-chicken-meat-will-be-as-good-as-the-real-thing|title=Betting Better Fake Chicken Meat Will Be As Good As The Real Thing|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Yuki Noguchi|date=May 17, 2012|publisher=NPR|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428200841/http://www.npr.org/blogs/thesalt/2012/05/17/152519988/a-farmer-bets-better-fake-chicken-meat-will-be-as-good-as-the-real-thing|dead-url=no}}</ref>

<span>2014年，《Fast Company</span>》雜誌將「超越肉類」公司評為最具創新實力的公司之一。而[[善待动物组织|善待動物組織]]則是將「超越肉類」公司點名為2013年善待動物組織的年度模範公司。<ref name="Chang2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/meet-the-man-behind-beyond-meat/|title=Meet the man behind "Beyond Meat" plant-based protein substitute|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Lulu Chang|date=Feb 7, 2014|publisher=cbsnews|archive-date=2017-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170421130435/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/meet-the-man-behind-beyond-meat/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Black2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.fastcompany.com/most-innovative-companies/2014/beyond-meat|title=43. Beyond Meat|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Jane Black|date=Feb 2, 2014|publisher=Fast Company|archive-date=2016-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160903110233/http://www.fastcompany.com/most-innovative-companies/2014/beyond-meat|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 超越肉類遍佈全美 ===
