從[[亚特兰大|亞特蘭大州]]起家的「熱帶冰沙餐飲」連鎖店（Tropical Smoothie Café）從2013年五月開始引進超越肉類的產品，將店裡菜單中含有雞肉的料理，推出「無雞肉」的純素選項供消費者選擇。<ref name="Gunther2013" /><ref name="Nguyen2013">{{cite web|url=http://vegnews.com/articles/page.do?pageId=5961&catId=8|title=Tropical Smoothie Café: Beyond Meat Here to Stay|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Melissa Nguyen|date=Jul 12, 2013|publisher=Veg News Daily|archive-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226092011/http://vegnews.com/articles/page.do?pageId=5961&catId=8|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Seward2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.ajc.com/news/business/tropical-smoothie-cafe-adds-beyond-meats-chicken/nXyD4/|title=Tropical Smoothie Café adds Beyond Meat’s ‘chicken’|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Christopher Seward|date=May 21, 2013|publisher=Atlanta Journal Constitution|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050219/http://www.ajc.com/news/business/tropical-smoothie-cafe-adds-beyond-meats-chicken/nXyD4/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 風投公司Obvious Corporation、比爾蓋茲以及其他投資者 ===
[[Twitter|Obvious Corporation]]是[[Twitter|Twitter]]的合夥創辦人[[埃文·威廉姆斯|埃文·威廉姆斯Evan Williams]],[[比兹·斯通|比茲·斯通]]、以及傑森‧高曼一起成立的風投公司。該公司2013年六月開始投入資金贊助「超越肉類」公司。<ref name="Etherington2013">{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/05/07/were-80-of-the-way-to-fake-meat-thats-indistinguishable-from-the-real-thing/|title=We’re 80% of the way to fake meat that’s indistinguishable from the real thing|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Darrell Etherington|date=May 7, 2013|publisher=TechCrunch|archive-date=2017-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170320045036/https://techcrunch.com/2013/05/07/were-80-of-the-way-to-fake-meat-thats-indistinguishable-from-the-real-thing/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Schwartz2012">{{cite web|url=http://www.fastcoexist.com/1680007/biz-stone-explains-why-twitters-co-founders-are-betting-big-on-a-vegan-meat-startup|title=Biz Stone Explains Why Twitter’s Co-Founders Are Betting Big on a Vegan Meat Startup|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=|date=Jun 13, 2012|publisher=|archive-date=2016-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818015542/http://www.fastcoexist.com/1680007/biz-stone-explains-why-twitters-co-founders-are-betting-big-on-a-vegan-meat-startup|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[比爾蓋茲|比爾‧蓋茲]]也在親身品嘗「超越肉類」公司的產品樣品之後，於2013年開始投資他們公司。比爾‧蓋茲表示:「我無法分辨超越肉類的無雞肉產品跟真的雞肉的差別」

同年，矽谷的風險投資公司[[凯鹏华盈|凱鵬華盈]]亦成為「超越肉類」的金主之一，這是凱鵬華盈的第一筆與食品相關的投資。美國人道主義協會也在「超越肉類」的投資者行列。2016年，[[泰森食品公司|泰森食品公司]]購入「超越肉類」百分之五的股份。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/11/business/tyson-foods-a-meat-leader-invests-in-protein-alternatives.html?_r=0|title=Tyson Foods, a Meat Leader, Invests in Protein Alternatives|date=10 October 2016|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=14 October 2016|last1=Strom|first1=Stephanie|archive-date=2017-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170221004232/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/10/11/business/tyson-foods-a-meat-leader-invests-in-protein-alternatives.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 創辦人伊森‧布朗 ==
在「超越肉類」創辦人伊森的成長過程中，小時候每個週末會到父親在[[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]]西半部的牛奶[[牧場|牧場]]度假，也就是因為有這樣的經歷，啟發他開始省思[[農場|農場]]裡的動物應有的對待和[[動物福利|福利]]。當伊森終於決定成為一位維根[[純素|純素]]者時，卻苦於市場上能夠找得到的肉類替代品非常有限，因此決定開始研究肉類替代品及其產業，最後終於成立了自己的公司。伊森在[[哥倫比亞大學|哥倫比亞大學]]獲得公共政策和工商管理碩士學位之後，曾經進入生產零排放質子交換膜燃料電池的[[巴拉德動力公司|巴拉德動力公司]]（BLDP）工作一段時間。在職期間，伊森因為對潔淨能源有了研究，才認知到畜牧業造成資源耗竭和氣候變遷的影響有多大。因此，決定轉換研究的重心，從能源轉換到食品。<ref name="Bessette2014">{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2014/01/31/10-questions-ethan-brown-ceo-beyond-meat/|title=10 Questions: Ethan Brown, CEO, Beyond Meat|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Chanelle Bessette|date=2014-01-31|publisher=Fortune|archive-date=2017-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170220192917/http://fortune.com/2014/01/31/10-questions-ethan-brown-ceo-beyond-meat/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年的《[[財星|財星]]》雜誌裡面有報導，伊森有提供一些動物福利團體資金援助，如「農場動物庇護所」（Farm Sanctuary）。

== 產品 ==
超越肉類公司研發和製作一系列以植物性蛋白為基底的食品。這些[[素肉|素肉]]是由大豆和豌豆分離蛋白、還有酵母和其他成分所組成。<ref name="Strom2014">{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/03/business/meat-alternatives-on-the-plate-and-in-the-portfolio.html?_r=1|title=Fake Meats, Finally, Taste Like Chicken|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Stephanie Strom|date=April 2, 2014|publisher=New York Times|archive-date=2017-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908063551/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/03/business/meat-alternatives-on-the-plate-and-in-the-portfolio.html?_r=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年，推出了「超越雞肉」和「超越牛肉」等系列商品。2015年則是推出一款不含[[大豆|大豆]]成分的純素維根漢堡排，命名為「野獸」。超越肉類的商品除了有零售包裝，同時也供應餐飲店業務食材製作成店內餐點。

=== 超越雞肉 ===
「超越肉類」的植物性無雞肉產品系列命名為「超越雞肉」，是將提煉之[[大豆|大豆]]和[[豌豆蛋白|豌豆蛋白]]混合、還有纖維和其他原料成分所製成，主打健康的雞肉替代品作為行銷訴求。他們混合所有原料，然後倒入食品擠壓機烹煮，由於擠壓機的機能有經過特別設計，透過蒸氣、擠壓和冷水處理，產品才能夠產生像雞肉一樣的質感。擠壓機處理完之後，再將產品切成型，加入調味，然後經過燒烤，最後才包裝完成。每一批純素雞柳需耗時約九十分鐘才能完成。

此仿雞肉之產品共有三種口味可以選擇:清淡口味、燒烤口味，以及美國西南醬口味素雞柳。<ref name="Brown2013" />

=== 超越牛肉 ===
「超越肉類」的仿細碎牛肉系列「超越牛肉」共有兩種口味：原味Beefy和勁辣Feisty。原料有[[豌豆蛋白|豌豆蛋白]]、[[菜籽油|菜籽油]]、以及各種調味香料。<ref name="Schwartz2012" /><ref name="beyondmeatbeefcrumbles">{{cite web|url=http://beyondmeat.com/beef-free-crumbles-beefy/|title=Beef-free crumbles|accessdate=7 July 2014|publisher=Beyond Meat|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711065115/http://beyondmeat.com/beef-free-crumbles-beefy/|archivedate=2014-07-11}}</ref>大豆及無麩質豌豆提煉蛋白的混合原料在未經過加熱和擠壓機的加工之前，是呈現膏體狀。<ref name="Manjoo2012" />

純素細碎牛肉每分量是55公克，其蛋白質含量跟同份量的傳統細碎牛肉是一樣的。<ref name="Gunther2013" /><ref name="Strom2014" />

=== 野獸 ===
[[File:Beyond_Meat_Beast_Burger_1.jpg|缩略图]]
超越肉類公司於2014年宣布開始研發和測試一款新產品，命名為「野獸」。他們邀請美國職棒大聯盟球隊[[紐約大都會|紐約大都會]]的球員在一場賽前活動進行嚐味測試，品嘗的就是這款以植物蛋白製作而成的純素漢堡排。<ref name="Nassauer2014">{{cite web|url=http://online.wsj.com/articles/meatless-burgers-make-their-mlb-pitch-1403736799|title=Meatless Burgers Make Their MLB Pitch|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Sarah Nassauer|date=2014-06-25|publisher=The Wall Street Journal|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022121448/http://online.wsj.com/articles/meatless-burgers-make-their-mlb-pitch-1403736799|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Just2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.ecorazzi.com/2014/07/18/beyond-meat-unleashes-new-beast-vegan-burger-on-ny-mets/|title=Beyond Meat Unleashes New ‘Beast’ Vegan Burger on NY Mets|accessdate=7 July 2014|date=7 July 2014|publisher=Ecorazzi|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908021828/http://www.ecorazzi.com/2014/07/18/beyond-meat-unleashes-new-beast-vegan-burger-on-ny-mets/|archive-date=2017-09-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="abc2014">{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/video/beast-burger-packs-flavor-nutrients-patty-24313619|title=Beast Burger Packs Flavor, Nutrients|accessdate=7 July 2014|date=7 July 2014|publisher=ABC News|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729041907/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/video/beast-burger-packs-flavor-nutrients-patty-24313619|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Dean2014">{{cite web|url=http://vegnews.com/articles/page.do?pageId=6485&catId=8|title=Beyond Meat Pitching Beast Burger to Big Leagues|accessdate=7 July 2014|date=7 July 2014|publisher=VegNews|archive-date=2017-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908020338/http://vegnews.com/articles/page.do?pageId=6485&catId=8|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年二月「野獸」純素漢堡排正式上市，且可以在美國各地的[[全食超市|全食超市]]購買到<ref name="Haber2015">{{cite web|url=http://nymag.com/next/2015/04/when-will-fake-meat-taste-like-real-meat.html|title=How Long Before Silicon Valley Can Produce Fake Meat That Tastes Like Real Meat?|accessdate=April 16, 2015|author=Haber, Matt|date=April 9, 2015|publisher=New York Magazine|archive-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330185927/http://nymag.com/next/2015/04/when-will-fake-meat-taste-like-real-meat.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。漢堡排的成分有:[[豌豆蛋白|豌豆蛋白]]粉、水、[[葵花油|葵花油]]，以及調合食用油（[[菜籽油|菜籽油]]、[[亞麻仁籽油|亞麻仁籽油]]、[[棕櫚油|棕櫚油]]、葵花油、DHA海藻油）。製程將所有原料放入雙軸擠壓機裡進行攪拌、烹煮和擠壓。擠壓機處理完之後，將產品做成漢堡排的形狀，最後送包裝成為零售食品。<ref name="Jacobsen2014">{{cite web|url=http://www.outsideonline.com/1928211/top-secret-food-will-change-way-you-eat?|title=The Top-Secret Food That Will Change the Way You Eat|accessdate=April 16, 2015|author=Jacobsen, Rowan|date=December 26, 2014|publisher=Outside Magazine|archive-date=2017-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321094833/https://www.outsideonline.com/1928211/top-secret-food-will-change-way-you-eat|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kumm2015">{{cite web|url=http://www.technologyreview.com/review/536296/the-problem-with-fake-meat/|title=The Problem with Fake Meat|accessdate=April 16, 2015|author=Kummer, Corby|date=March 31, 2015|publisher=MIT Technology Review|archive-date=2015-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212181709/http://www.technologyreview.com/review/536296/the-problem-with-fake-meat/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

漢堡排是維根[[純素|純素]]，且無大豆成分；蛋白質含量是23克，含有抗氧化營養素、鐵質、鈣質、維生素B6、B12和D、鉀、[[二十二碳六烯酸|DHA]]和[[Α-亞麻酸|ALA]][[Omega-3脂肪酸|Omega-3脂肪酸]]。<ref name="Angle2015">{{cite web|url=http://www.shape.com/healthy-eating/meal-ideas/beyond-meat-s-high-protein-veggie-burger-best-thing-ever-happen-vegans|title=Beyond Meat’s High-Protein Veggie Burger Is the Best Thing to Ever Happen to Vegans|accessdate=April 16, 2015|author=Angle, Sara and Rachel Schultz|date=February 13, 2015|publisher=Shape Magazine|archive-date=2017-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409033241/http://www.shape.com/healthy-eating/meal-ideas/beyond-meat-s-high-protein-veggie-burger-best-thing-ever-happen-vegans|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="beyond2015">{{cite web|url=http://beyondmeat.com/products/view/the-beast-burger|title=The Beast Burger|accessdate=April 16, 2015|author=|date=April 2015|publisher=Beyond Meat|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415065042/http://beyondmeat.com/products/view/the-beast-burger|archive-date=2015-04-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Joiner2015">{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/01/15/the-veggie-burgers-with-meaty-ambition.html|title=The Veggie Burgers With Meaty Ambition|accessdate=April 16, 2015|author=Joiner, James|date=January 15, 2015|publisher=The Daily Beast|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223012230/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/01/15/the-veggie-burgers-with-meaty-ambition.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 超越漢堡肉 ===
2016年五月，「超越肉類」推出第一款以植物蛋白為基底的純素漢堡肉，用來放置在零售商店的肉品區與一般牛肉、雞肉、豬肉並列展示販售。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/23/business/plant-based-the-beyond-burger-aims-to-stand-sturdy-among-meat.html|title=Plant-Based, the Beyond Burger Aims to Stand Sturdy Among Meat|last=Strom|first=Stephanie|date=2016-05-22|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-10-27|archive-date=2016-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012125224/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/23/business/plant-based-the-beyond-burger-aims-to-stand-sturdy-among-meat.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>此商品第一次上架的點是在位於[[科羅拉多州|科羅拉多州]][[波德_(科羅拉多州)|波德市]]珍珠街上的[[全食超市|全食超市]]。「超越漢堡肉」在上架的短短一個小時內就全數被搶空。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/business/ct-beyond-burger-20160524-story.html|title=Meatless burger that bleeds beet juice sells out in an hour at its Whole Foods debut|last=Tribune|first=Chicago|newspaper=chicagotribune.com|access-date=2016-10-27|archive-date=2016-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161028005342/http://www.chicagotribune.com/business/ct-beyond-burger-20160524-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

一份「超越漢堡肉」含有20克的蛋白質，且成分中不含大豆、[[麸质|麩質]]、基因改造成分，且無膽固醇，他的[[飽和脂肪|飽和脂肪]]含量是傳統瘦肉肥肉比80:20的牛肉漢堡排的一半。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.beyondmeat.com/products/view/beyond-burger|title=The Beyond Burger™ {{!}} The Beyond Burger™ {{!}} Beyond Meat - The Future of Protein™|website=www.beyondmeat.com|access-date=2016-10-27|archive-date=2016-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161027213812/http://beyondmeat.com/products/view/beyond-burger|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170408/1093847/?utm_source=FB&utm_medium=MWeb_Share&utm_campaign=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170408%2F1093847%2F|title=比爾蓋茲賣「未來漢堡」　粉嫩噴汁香到肚子餓|newspaper=蘋果日報|access-date=2017-04-08}}</ref>

== 生產量 ==
「超越肉類」的工廠位在[[密蘇里州|密蘇里州]]的[[哥倫比亞_(密蘇里州)|哥倫比亞]]市。<ref name="Foster2013">{{cite web|url=http://www.popsci.com/article/science/can-artificial-meat-save-world|title=Can Artificial Meat Save the World|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Tom Foster|date=2013-11-18|publisher=Popular Science|archive-date=2017-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223060103/http://www.popsci.com/article/science/can-artificial-meat-save-world|dead-url=no}}</ref>廠房一年的產能可以生產約七百萬磅（三百萬公斤）雞肉替代品。

== 品牌名聲 ==
「超越肉類」的產品在市場上獲得一些評價，如《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》美食評論作家馬克·彼特曼做過這樣的評論：「你根本吃不出超越肉類的產品和真的雞肉有何差別，至少以此（評論美食）為生的我是這樣認為。」<ref name="Wellman2012">{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-2159300/New-vegan-chicken-product-sells-days-entices-meat-lovers-promise-authentic-texture-flavour.html|title=New vegan 'chicken' sells out in days with promise of authentic texture and taste... but can it impress our meat-loving tester?|accessdate=7 July 2014|author=Wellman, Victoria|date=7 July 2014|publisher=The Daily Mail|archive-date=2016-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226033801/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/femail/article-2159300/New-vegan-chicken-product-sells-days-entices-meat-lovers-promise-authentic-texture-flavour.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[比爾·蓋茲|比爾·蓋茲]]在個人的[[網誌|網誌]]也寫到：「我吃不出超越肉類產品和真的雞肉的差別。」<ref name="Foster2013" />2013年，名廚暨美食節目主持人奧爾頓·布朗對超越肉類的「超越雞肉」產品如此評論：「這是我吃過最像肉的仿肉食品。」<ref name="Brown2013" />

